com.brownian.morse.receivers

Class MorseToMidiReceiverAsync

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brownian.morse.receivers.MorseToMidiReceiverAsync
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MorseReceiver, MorseReceiverAsync

    public class MorseToMidiReceiverAsync
extends java.lang.Object
implements MorseReceiverAsync
    A class that receives Morse symbols, translates them to MIDI instructions, and passes those to a MIDI Receiver (on Channel 0). This class is not thread-safe; if receiving from multiple sources, symbols should be sent to it inside synchronized blocks.

        public MorseToMidiReceiverAsync(javax.sound.midi.Receiver midiReceiver)
